data.description: Contemporary Farmhouse Perfection!   Builder's Warranty will transfer and Assumable 5.625 VA rate available to approved buyers. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath luxury home is Cover ready with style and details galore. The tray ceilings and large windows make the 1,892 square feet of living space larger than life. The neutral color palette, wood burning fireplace and beautiful wood accents throughout create a warm welcome home. The Large primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom has a large soaking tub, tiled stand-alone shower, dual sinks and large walk-in closet. One of the remaining 3 bedrooms is conveniently located off the living area making it a wonderful home office or playroom option.  All bedrooms come with custom closets making wardrobe storage a breeze. The open concept kitchen has stainless steel appliances, quartz counters and an extended island design. Outside, the style continues with a large, covered patio with additional storage, perfect to unwind or to entertain friends and family.
